text: If do_import_module is called without a modname argument, it will try to access self.modname on the underlying node, but Import nodes don't have a modname attribute, so it will raise an AttributeError.
title: ImportFromMixin is used in both Import and ImportFrom nodes, but do_import_module doesn't work for Import
